Comment: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:46.76,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,EBISU TOWN
Comment: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.43,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,PRISON
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,This is what everyone's \Ntalking about in the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I got excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Will the decisive battle start soon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,He knocked him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:32.75,Main,,0,0,0,,If this is something that you want to do,...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:36.55,Main,,0,0,0,,...maybe I can help you a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Teach me! That's exactly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:57.48,Main,,0,0,0,,That Grandpa did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandpa! That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,How did you use Haki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It's too much for an old body...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:25.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Go! Madilloman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:50.91,Translation Info,,0,0,0,,流桜 Ryuo, Flowing Sakura
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:50.91,Main,,0,0,0,,You call it Haki,\Nbut we call it Ryuo in the Wano Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ryuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It has the meaning of "flow."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:04.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your Haki flows in your body, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:08.14,Main,,0,0,0,,First, feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Flowing Haki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't press too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:48.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Allow the unused Haki in your body\Nto flow to your fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:55.02,Main,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:03.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring in more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Go to hell, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:25.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Kick the Grandpa's ass, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Push them against the \Nwall already, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:50.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm starving to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,How long will it take to \Nget there, Okiku-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:59.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I think we will enter Udon sometime tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:04.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It's taking so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:16.27,Translation Info,,0,0,0,,お汁粉 Oshiruko, Red-Bean Soup
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:16.27,Main,,0,0,0,,The sweet, sweet Oshiruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.86,Main,,0,0,0,,The Oshiruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:36.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I see, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:59.52,Main,,0,0,0,,By seeing this flyer,\Nwe learned about the great battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:05.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Two birds on fire...\NThat means twilight on the day of the Fire Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:09.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The rendezvous point for the raid\Nis Habu Port!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:13.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kin'emon-kun must've given\Na lot of thought to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon... kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:28.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I understand.\NIt's no wonder that you have a glum look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.55,Main,,0,0,0,,The plan is ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Even the enemies know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:38.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm... That is right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:43.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Our allies with the Reversed \NCrescent Moon tattoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.69,Main,,0,0,0,,...signifying rebellion are getting \Ncaught one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:52.49,Main,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice to take it back\Nand say, "It was all fake,"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...but then it'll mislead your allies, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:02.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Before this, however, I didn't know about\Nthe crescent moon ankle tattoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You were able to secure allies like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:11.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are tons of people\Nwho got motivated by seeing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Please tell Kin'emon-kun and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:24.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That we'll fight along with you at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon... kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you two, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, it's getting busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:47.21,Main,,0,0,0,,There are tons of people\Nwho won't last the week before the great battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.30,Main,,0,0,0,,So if you'll excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,A handsome man,...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.01,Main,,0,0,0,,...a beautiful woman,...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.43,Main,,0,0,0,,...and a town girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, good to see you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, who's that Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:20.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I was listening, but I couldn't tell\Nhow you guys are connected to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, he was quite cheerful!\NWho is that Tonoyasu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yasu-san! Play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.76,Main,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I must say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.57,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You were talking to him\Nnot knowing who he was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, he just went on and on, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.08,Main,,0,0,0,,How could you forget someone like him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, since he addressed \Nus with "kun" and "chan"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:11.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought if he had been someone important in the past,\Nit would be rude to ask him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:16.01,Main,,0,0,0,,He was addressing you casually,\Nso could he be your childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Or an instructor of some kind?\NOr an older friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:28.10,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:33.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Gramps, Gramps, how's the abdominal pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yasu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.05,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.55,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't it, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,My Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not flowing to my fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:29.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa, he took down too many, that idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:39.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Haki won't flow to an angry fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:44.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:08.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you as always.\NMy body feels heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not that much,\Nbut I brought you some millet and water!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.92,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll give you energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:18.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You're such a nice person, Yasu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:23.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You're good at praising!\NI'm so happy to be called a nice person!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give you two more millet grains!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll leave them here, so don't forget to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:33.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Yasu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:36.90,Main,,0,0,0,,See you, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Seaweed Shop Granny!\NDo you have enough medicine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,No, but just seeing you cheers me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You're such a man-killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:51.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, mister, how's your knee?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yasu-san! Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:57.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanko! How's your sick mother doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Osaki-san, how's your baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:04.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Up, up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Yasu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Come see us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, everyone! Take these!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:16.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Tonoyasu must be making a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.52,Main,,0,0,0,,No one else can give out food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.23,Main,,0,0,0,,No, he is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,He only gets paid peanuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:30.49,Main,,0,0,0,,His only daughter named Toko-chan\Nwas sold to the capital and has been working there,...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:35.46,Main,,0,0,0,,...but she sends most of her \Nearnings to Yasu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Toko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.80,Past,,0,0,0,,I'm not otoko (male)!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It must be her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:47.97,Main,,0,0,0,,He said Toko-chan took the trouble\Nto send it,...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,...so he shouldn't have it all to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:55.31,Main,,0,0,0,,He gives out food to those who can't work\Nevery day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,He doesn't eat much himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,His facial expressions and body movements are so goofy,\Nbut everyone's always loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.74,Main,,0,0,0,,He's a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.13,Past,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:30.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's bedtime! Go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Continue this again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:40.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me fight more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:52.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Won't you even let me eat something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop barking like a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up and go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become a mummy by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something, Straw Hat Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.09,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:10.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would you want to fight Kaido?!\NI heard you once lost to him in Kuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,They're annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.75,Translation Info,,0,0,0,,四皇 Yonko, Four Emperors
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know the Yonko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.96,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:45.38,Main,,0,0,0,,There are four great pirates\Ncalled emperors across the world,...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.59,Main,,0,0,0,,...and Kaido is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:53.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of Pirates,...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,...so I have to take them all down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:58.39,Main,,0,0,0,,The King of Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.52,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean a man like Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know Gold Roger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,He came to this country a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what Kin'emon said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:15.87,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Kin'emon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you know that name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:28.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:34.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You're... R-Raizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.23,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Raizo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:58.08,Main,,0,0,0,,How are you alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Raizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:03.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me explain, Hyogoro-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest! You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,There he is! Ushimitsu Kozo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:19.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it true, Raizo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:28.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I... cannot believe...\Nthat you're the famous Hyogoro-dono...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.90,Main,,0,0,0,,This is hard to take in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that you really crossed through\N20 years of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,...and came from the Wano Country on that fateful day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:43.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! By Toki-sama's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you, Caribou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:56.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Please don't say that, Straw Hat-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Raizo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:02.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You thought it was the key to my cuffs,\Nbut it was to his?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't hate me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:09.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I may come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:13.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm your subordinate from now on, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:18.53,Main,,0,0,0,,But, in exchange,...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,...let me get on board when you're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:24.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're stuck here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:28.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for what I did to you in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I have changed now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:38.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, there's no problem if you've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:45.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you... very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:50.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of trap?!\NIt scares me how easy that was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:55.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffytaro-dono!\NThis guy has quite an interesting power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.86,Main,,0,0,0,,He could be useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:04.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Without giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.58,Main,,0,0,0,,greedily...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I held on to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Hyogoro-dono?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.14,Main,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:26.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I was only gonna \Ndie miserably here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I was accepting my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Had this not happened,\NI would've died...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.49,Main,,0,0,0,,...not knowing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,So the Akazaya samurai are alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Oden's son, Kozuki Momonosuke, is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,The fire of rebellion....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.79,Main,,0,0,0,,...isn't extinguished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Raizo! Straw Hat Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:13.31,Main,,0,0,0,,When it comes to this,\Neven a dotard like me still can contribute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:17.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you please let me join you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:20.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, we could ask for none better than him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-dono! He used to be the greatest yakuza boss\Nin the Wano Country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:30.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! I knew you were a big deal back\Nin the day, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:36.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You said that you were recruiting allies\Nin the Flower Capital now, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:41.97,Main,,0,0,0,,It's surely fate that brought you to Udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,In this Prisoner Mine,...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:48.51,Main,,0,0,0,,...there are four other excavation sites\Njust as large as this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:53.23,Main,,0,0,0,,There are tens of thousands \Nof prisoners in Udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,However, not everyone was imprisoned\Nfor robbery or assault...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Most of the prisoners are here for...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:04.24,Main,,0,0,0,,...treason against Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:07.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! Why didn't I think of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Rage from across the country is pooled here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:17.17,Main,,0,0,0,,The yakuza bosses who once supported the Wano Country\Nbehind the scenes are all here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:22.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to them!\NI'm sure they'll be happy to fight for Kozuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:25.59,Main,,0,0,0,,And Raizo! In that cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:27.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:33.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I have had a word with Kawamatsu.\NI will release him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:35.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:38.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Then if I break this place down,...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,...everyone will ally with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:45.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-dono! You are too loud!\NIt is not that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:50.49,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! Our plan has been set!\NBring me something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:21:59.63,Main,,0,0,0,,When did you get that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yum-yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Oshiruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:09.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you got to have some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:19.48,Main,,0,0,0,,...eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:24.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry... and tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:28.11,Main,,0,0,0,,No Oshiruko yet? Okiku-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:33.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Sharkodile-san is exhausted, too.\NBut we have already entered Udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:39.92,Main,,0,0,0,,My Oshiruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:43.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this really a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:49.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:51.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Another bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.30,0:22:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oshiruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:05.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stuff myself silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:11.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,News of the Flower Capital's beloved \NUshimitsu Kozo who sides with the weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:13.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and crushes the strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:16.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...spreads like wildfire \Nacross the Wano Country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:19.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, after meeting up with Brook,...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:25.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Zoro and the others learn about\NOrochi's despicable plot and a cruel truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:27.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:30.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Meet Easily! \NIdentity of Ushimitsu Kozo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.85,0:23:33.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
